<p>9 Dec, Leicester, <a href="https://eastmidslt.wordpress.com/2015/09/29/call-for-presentations-emlt-winter-2015-meeting/">East Midlands Learning Technologists&rsquo; Group: Using Technology to Support Assessment</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>9 Dec, London, <a href="http://www.moderngov.com/courses/personal-skills/effective-data-visualisation-09-12-15/">Effective Data Visualisation</a>.&nbsp; [ModernGov]</p>
