</li>
<li>
<p><a href="http://venturebeat.com/2015/07/23/linkedin-quietly-removes-option-to-export-contacts-makes-users-wait-up-to-72-hours-for-their-data-archive/">LinkedIn has removed the option to export your contacts</a>. &nbsp;Users can request an archive of their data, which may take up to 72 hours to complete.&nbsp; [Venture Beat]</p>
