</li>
<li>
<p>7-9 Aug, Online, <a href="https://www.wiziq.com/course/74432-moodle-moot-for-2015-mmvc15">2015 Moodle Moot Virtual Conference (MMVC)</a>.&nbsp; [Clayton Wright]</p>
</li>
