</li>
<li>
<p>5-7 Sep, York, <a href="http://www.sfep.org.uk/pub/confs/conferences.asp">SfEP/SI 1<sup>st</sup> Annual Joint Conference</a>.&nbsp; [SFEP]</p>
</li>
