</li>
<li>
<p>9-11 Sep, London, <a href="http://www.alpsp.org/Ebusiness/TrainingAndEvents/ALPSPInternationalConference.aspx?ID=394">Association of Learned &amp; Professional Society Publishers Annual Conference and Awards</a>.&nbsp; [Clayton Wright]</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>10-11 Sep, Paisley, <a href="http://www.uws.ac.uk/heir2015/">Higher Education Institutional Research Network 8<sup>th</sup> Annual Conference</a>.&nbsp; [Clayton Wright]</p>
</li>
