</li>
<li>
<p>29 Apr, London, <a href="http://www.westminsterforumprojects.co.uk/forums/event.php?eid=948">The future for graduate employability: careers services, curriculum design and employer engagement</a>.&nbsp; [Westminster HEF]</p>
</li>
