<p><strong>And Finally&hellip;</strong></p>
<p>R.I.P. Professor Paul Clark.</p>
<p>I&rsquo;ve lost track of whether the original idea for our OU e-Learning Community came from Paul or Chris Pegler, but I do know he was a staunch supporter from the outset.&nbsp; Rest in peace.</p>
