<li>12-14 Nov, Manchester, <a href="http://www.ucisa.ac.uk/groups/cisg/Events/2014/cisg2014.aspx">CISG14 Annual Conference and Exhibition</a>.&nbsp; [Clayton Wright]</li>
<li>13-14 Nov, Online, <a href="http://www.elearningguild.com/online-forums/content/3549/online-forums-2014---making-learning-memorable-with-graphics-and-visual-design-november-13--14/">Making Learning Memorable with Graphics and Visual Design</a>.&nbsp; [Clayton Wright]</li>
<li>13-14, Nottingham, <a href="http://seda.ac.uk/?p=14_2&e=450">19<sup>th</sup> Annual SEDA Conference: Opportunities and challenges for academic development in a post-digital age</a>.&nbsp; [Clayton Wright]</li>
