<li>15 Nov, York, <a href="https://www.llas.ac.uk/events/6915">Making Video for Language Learning and Teaching</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</li>
<li>17-21 Nov, Online, <a href="http://www.globaleducationconference.com/">Globaledcon: Connecting Educators And Organizations Worldwide</a>.&nbsp; [Clayton Wright]</li>
<li>20-21 Nov, London, <a href="http://www3.imperial.ac.uk/cpd/courses/subject/medical/momed/schedule">Mobile Medical Education - Successful Implementation in Practice</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</li>
