<li>27 Nov, London, <a href="http://www.westminsterforumprojects.co.uk/forums/event.php?eid=830">Innovative approaches to curriculum design and delivery in Higher Education</a>.&nbsp; [Westminster Forum]</li>
<li>28 Nov, London, <a href="http://www.elearningnetwork.org/events/social-and-informal-learning">Social and informal learning</a>.&nbsp; [e.learning age]</li>
