<li>And McDonalds allows you to pick and run your own <a href="http://en.mcdonalds.fantasy.fifa.com/">fantasy World Cup team</a></li>
</ul>
<p>But if you have no interest whatsoever in football, you might be entertained by these <a href="http://www.cultofmac.com/280795/watching-kids-trying-figure-use-old-apple-ii-totally-hilarious/">kids trying to work out how to use an old Apple II computer</a>.</p>]]></description>
