<li>26 Jun, Hendon, <a href="http://www.heacademy.ac.uk/events/detail/2014/Workshop/HSC/26-06-14-SocialMedia2">e-Pedagogy, e-Learning and Blended Learning: From Flipped to Global Classroom and MOOCs</a>.&nbsp; [HEA]</li>
<li>30 Jun-4 Jul, Online, <a href="http://learn1.open.ac.uk/course/view.php?id=100074">Student Connections: the first online conference for social science students</a>.&nbsp; [Dave Middleton]</li>
