<li>1 Apr, Webinar, <a href="https://www.alt.ac.uk/civicrm/event/info?id=95&reset=1">The Digital Student &ndash; Understanding Student expectations and experiences of the digital environment</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</li>
<li>2 Apr, Webinar, <a href="http://jiscevents.force.com/E/EventsDetailPage?id=a06U000000GPQSfIAP&srvc=JISC RSC UK">Nybbles, bits and bytes &ndash; lights, camera, action</a>.&nbsp; [JISC]</li>
<li>2 Apr, Liverpool, <a href="http://www.heacademy.ac.uk/events/detail/2014/Seminars/AH/GEN913_LJMU">Digital Literacies: Building Learning Communities in the Humanities</a>.&nbsp; [HEA]</li>
