<li>29 Apr, London, <a href="http://www.insidegovernment.co.uk/event-details/higher-education-marketing/271">The Future of Higher Education Marketing 2014</a>.&nbsp; [Inside Government]</li>
<li>29-30 Apr, Birmingham, <a href="http://www.neilstewartassociates.com/jb358/">The Association of Business Schools 3<sup>rd</sup> Annual Learning and Teaching Conference</a>.&nbsp; [NSA]</li>
<li>30 Apr-1 May, London, <a href="http://www.cipd.co.uk/events/learning-development-show">CIPD Learning &amp; Development Conference and Exhibition</a>.&nbsp; [CIPD]</li>
<li>6 May, Walton Hall, <a href="http://www.open.ac.uk/about/teaching-and-learning/esteem/">eSTEeM Annual Conference &ndash; Reflecting on Teaching and Learning</a>.&nbsp;</li>
