<p><em>[Huffington Post; Students Last]</em></p>
<p>The debate continues: is a degree really worth the investment?&nbsp; This promotional video from <a href="http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/02/24/honest-university-commercial_n_4847110.html">EveRy University</a> should leave you in no doubt</p>
<p>And can this be true?&nbsp; Has <a href="http://studentslast.blogspot.co.uk/2014/02/pearson-buys-new-york-state-education.html">Pearson</a> finally taken over the New York State Education Department?</p>]]></description>
