<li>2 Apr, Liverpool, <a href="http://www.heacademy.ac.uk/events/detail/2014/Seminars/AH/GEN913_LJMU">Digital Literacies: Building Learning Communities in the Humanities</a>.&nbsp; [HEA]</li>
