              <title>e-Learning Digest No 113 - Jan 14</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/8529</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/8529</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>UK </strong><strong>Conferences &amp; Workshops </strong></p>
