<li>5 Feb, Bournemouth, <a href="http://www.heacademy.ac.uk/events/detail/2014/Seminars/Social_Sciences/GEN825_bournemouth">Exploring the value of social media for education and research in business and management studies</a>.&nbsp; [HEA]</li>
