<li>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 14 Jan, Huddersfield, <a href="http://www.heacademy.ac.uk/events/detail/2014/Seminars/AH/GEN939_University_of_Huddersfield">Interdisciplinary Imaginations &ndash; using creative methodologies to solve &lsquo;wicked problems&rsquo;</a>.&nbsp; [HEA]</li>
