<li>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 23 Jan, London, <a href="http://www.hefce.ac.uk/news/events/events82788.html">The future of postgraduate taught education</a>.&nbsp; [HEFCE]</li>
<li>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 23-24 Jan, Online, <a href="http://www.elearningguild.com/online-forums/content/3121/online-forums-2014---development-tips-and-techniques-for-instructional-designers-jan-23--24/">Development Tips and Techniques for Instructional Designers</a>.&nbsp; [Clayton Wright]</li>
<li>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 23-24 Jan, Southampton, <a href="https://www.llas.ac.uk/events/6848">e-learning symposium 2014</a>.&nbsp; [e-Learning Centre]</li>
<li>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 27 Jan&ndash;7 Mar, Online, <a href="http://www.brookes.ac.uk/services/ocsld/online/first_steps/">First steps into learning and teaching in higher education</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</li>
