<li>11 Dec, London, <a href="http://www.niace.org.uk/campaigns-events/events/learning-at-the-digital-frontier">NIACE annual digital learning conference: Learning at the Digital Frontier</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</li>
<li>14 Jan, Huddersfield, <a href="http://www.heacademy.ac.uk/events/detail/2014/Seminars/AH/GEN939_University_of_Huddersfield">Interdisciplinary Imaginations &ndash; using creative methodologies to solve &lsquo;wicked problems&rsquo;</a>.&nbsp; [HEA]</li>
<li>16 Jan, London, <a href="http://www.hefce.ac.uk/news/events/events82787.html">The student academic experience - expectations, engagement and complaint resolution</a>.&nbsp; [HEFCE]</li>
