<li>4-24 Nov, Online, <a href="http://lak13.learning-analytics.info/">Introduction to Learning Analytics &amp; Techniques</a>.&nbsp; [George Siemens]</li>
<li>4 Nov-4 Dec, Online, <a href="http://www.brookes.ac.uk/services/ocsld/online/designing_online_course/">Designing your online course</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</li>
<li>7 Nov, London, <a href="http://www.hefce.ac.uk/news/events/events83189.html">Implementing the national access strategy: charting the future direction of widening access</a>.&nbsp; [HEFCE]</li>
<li>12 Nov, York, <a href="http://www.heacademy.ac.uk/events/detail/2013/12_Nov_Webinar_York">Higher education for the future: flexible pedagogies that empower learners for complexity, uncertainty and change</a>.&nbsp; [HEA]</li>
<li>13 Nov, London, <a href="http://www.insidegovernment.co.uk/event-details/postgraduate-education/221">Postgraduate Education 2013: Improving Access, Funding and Outcomes</a>.&nbsp; [Inside Government]</li>
<li>14 Nov, London, <a href="http://www.hefce.ac.uk/news/events/events83014.html">UK universities and research competitiveness: the future for UK research policy and funding</a>.&nbsp; [HEFCE]</li>
