<li>1 Oct, London, <a href="http://www.aoc.co.uk/en/briefings/briefings-2013/events/events-1213--aoc-create-events--new-academic-year-new-events.cfm">Association of Colleges Learning Technology Conference 2013</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</li>
<li>1 Oct, Webinar, <a href="http://www.bersin.com/News/EventDetails.aspx?id=16807&mkt_tok=3RkMMJWWfF9wsRonua3Nde/hmjTEU5z16u0lW6KzlMI/0ER3fOvrPUfGjI4ATsFrNa+TFAwTG5toziV8R7nCKs1s18UQXRjr">The Changing State of High-Impact Learning in the UK and Europe</a>.&nbsp; [Bersin by Delloite]</li>
