              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/6483</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/6483</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>UK </strong><strong>Conferences &amp; Workshops </strong></p>
