<li>19 Oct, London, <a href="http://blogs.city.ac.uk/care/ar-event/">Augmented Reality in Education</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</li>
<li>23 Oct, London, <a href="http://www.neilstewartassociates.com/jb332/">Part time distance and flexible study in HE</a>.&nbsp; [Neil Stewart Associates]</li>
<li>23-24 Oct, Nottingham, <a href="http://festival.gamecity.org/">Interactive Technologies and Games: Education, Health and Disability</a> (part of GameCity festival).&nbsp; [Sara Hack]</li>
<li>29-31 Oct, London, <a href="http://www.internet-librarian.com/2012/">Internet Librarian International 2012: Re-image, Renew, Reboot &ndash; Innovating for Success</a>.&nbsp; [Clayton Wright]</li>
<li>1-2 Nov, London, <a href="http://www.computerbasedmath.org/events/londonsummit2012/">The Computer-Based Math Education Summit</a>.&nbsp; [Wolfram Insider]</li>
