<li>12-14 Sep, Birmingham, <a href="http://hci2012.bcs.org/">HCI 2012: People and Computers</a>.&nbsp; [Martyn Cooper]</li>
<li>13-14 Sep, Online, <a href="http://www.elearningguild.com/online-forums/content/2299/online-forums-2012---development--implementation-sep-13--14/">eLearning Development and Implementation: Best Practices</a>.&nbsp; [eLearning Guild]</li>
<li>13-14 Sep, Cork, <a href="http://academic-conferences.org/ecime/ecime2012/ecime12-home.htm">6<sup>th</sup> European Conference on Information Management and Evaluation (ECIME)</a>.&nbsp; [Clayton Wright]</li>
