<li>12 Jul, London, <a href="http://www.insidegovernment.co.uk/other/apps/">Apps in the Public Sector: Opportunities and Threats</a>.&nbsp; [Inside Government]</li>
<li>16-17 Jul, Bolton, <a href="http://www.bolton.ac.uk/conferences/cycomp2012/">Cyberpsychology and Computer Psychology Conference 2012</a>.&nbsp; [Clayton Wright]</li>
<li>20 Jul, Birmingham, <a href="http://www.heacademy.ac.uk/events/detail/2012/OER/OER_SEDA_CONFERENCE">HEA/SEDA Conference: Open Horizons: Sharing the future</a>.&nbsp; [HEA]</li>
