<li>12-13 Apr, London, <a href="http://www.heacademy.ac.uk/events/detail/2012/academyevents/STEM_annual_conf">2012 STEM Annual Conference: Aiming for Excellence in STEM Learning and Teaching</a>.&nbsp; [Clayton Wright]</li>
<li>16 Apr, London, <a href="http://www.neilstewartassociates.com/jb321/">International Partnerships: Delivering quality Higher Education worldwide</a>.&nbsp; [Neil Stewart Associates]</li>
<li>16-18 Apr, Cambridge, <a href="http://www8.open.ac.uk/score/events/cambridge-2012">OpenCourseWare Consortium Global 2012/OER 12 Conference</a>.&nbsp; [SCORE]</li>
