              <title>e-Learning Digest No 85 - Sep 11</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/5723</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/5723</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>UK </strong><strong>Conferences &amp; Workshops </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>5 Oct, Online, <a href="http://www.enspire.com/mobile-learning-and-france.html">Mobile Learning: The Low Hanging Fruit</a>.&nbsp; [enspire learning]</li>
<li>6-7 Oct, Online, <a href="http://www.elearningguild.com/online-forums/content/1854/2011-olf---oct-6--7">Web 2.0 and Web 3.0: Best Practices</a>.&nbsp; [eLearning Guild]</li>
<li>10 Oct, Online, <a href="http://www.alt.ac.uk/events/getting-started-serious-games">ALT/ELN webinar: Getting started with serious games</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</li>
