<li>15-16 Sep, Aberdeen, <a href="http://academic-conferences.org/ecie/ecie2011/ecie11-home.htm">2011 European Conference on Innovation and Entrepreneurship (ECIE)</a>.&nbsp; [Clayton Wright]</li>
