<li>13-15 Sep, Oxford, <a href="http://www.cfbt.com/UKFIET/">2011 International Conference on Education and Development</a>.&nbsp; [Clayton Wright]</li>
<li>15 Sep, London, <a href="http://www.neilstewartassociates.com/jb309">Access to Higher Education: Raising levels of attainment; widening participation</a>.&nbsp; [Neil Stewart Associates]</li>
<li>15 Sep, Online, <a href="http://www.alt.ac.uk/events/interview-top-designer">ALT/ELN webinar: Interview with a top designer</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</li>
<li>15-16 Sep, Aberdeen, <a href="http://academic-conferences.org/ecie/ecie2011/ecie11-home.htm">2011 European Conference on Innovation and Entrepreneurship (ECIE)</a>.&nbsp; [Clayton Wright]</li>
