              <title>e-Learning Digest No 69 - May 10</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/3672</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/3672</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>OU Annual Conference</strong></p>
<p>This year&rsquo;s annual OU annual conference - Learning in the Open World - is being held entirely online on <strong>22 &amp; 23 Jun</strong>.&nbsp; We hope this will make it easier for people to &lsquo;attend&rsquo; specific sessions, particularly those based outside Walton Hall for whom distance may have been an issue in previous years.&nbsp; We also hope to encourage some staff to dip a first toe in the water of online collaboration and communication tools such as Elluminate.&nbsp; To find out more, your first port of call should be the <a href="/cloudscape/view/2012">conference Cloudworks page</a>, where you can register your interest by clicking the 'Mark as attending' button.&nbsp; More detailed conference information will follow over the coming month.</p>
<p>[Martin Weller]</p>
<p>~~~~~~~~&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>UK </strong><strong>Conferences &amp; Workshops </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>3 Jun, Edge Hill, <a href="http://www.edgehill.ac.uk/solstice/Conference2010/programme.html">SOLSTICE: Technology Enhanced Learning and the Student Experience</a>.&nbsp; [Liz Mallett]</li>
<li>9-10 Jun, Telford, <a href="http://www.pebblepad.co.uk/conference.asp">PebblePad personal learning systems conference</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</li>
<li>10 Jun, Walton Hall, <a href="http://www.thebild.org/Events/UpcomingEvents/HJTOPU">Learning and development - the next five years</a>.&nbsp; [BILD]</li>
<li>10 Jun, Leeds, <a href="http://www.rsc-yh.ac.uk/conference/index.asp">Yorks &amp; Humberside e-Learning Conference 2010: Active Learning</a>.&nbsp; [JE]</li>
<li>15 Jun, Bolton, <a href="http://wiki.cetis.ac.uk/Mobile_Tech_Meeting_15th_June_2010">JISC CETIS meeting on Mobile Technologies</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</li>
<li>16-17 Jun, Hatfield, <a href="http://www.herts.ac.uk/about-us/learning-and-teaching/learning-teaching-institute/conferences/blended-learning-conference-2010/home.cfm">Fifth International Blended Learning Conference</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</li>
<li>23 Jun, London, <a href="http://insidegovernment.msgfocus.com/c/1sOmZjL7DXFBu8wXe">Tackling Social Exclusion Through Technology: Delivering Digital Inclusion</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</li>
<li>24 Jun, London, <a href="http://www.westminsterforumprojects.co.uk/forums/agenda/future-of-universities-agenda.pdf">The Future of Universities - Funding and Access Seminar</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</li>
<li>25 Jun, Edinburgh, <a href="http://uk-sself.ning.com/events/challenge-2-session-learning">HEA SIG - Learning and assessment &lsquo;born digital</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</li>
<li>28-29 Jun, Middlesbrough, <a href="http://www.tees.ac.uk/sections/research/social_futures/events_details.cfm?event_id=2851">Immersive Technologies for Learning</a>.&nbsp; [ALT]</li>
<li>28-30 Jun, London, <strong><a href="http://www.i-society.eu/">International Conference on Information Society (i-Society 2010)</a>.&nbsp; [JE]</strong><strong></strong></li>
